"title": "7726: evangelists, ministry of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7726",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Evangelists proclaim the good news of Jesus Christ, calling those who hear to believe in him. This may be in the context of missionary journeys, often in partnership with others, or within a more settled ministry. Carrying out the task requires integrity and commitment in the face of hardships and danger; it also brings joy at seeing the church grow.</p>\n<h2>The task of evangelists</h2>\n<h3>Announcing good news</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7\">ISA 52:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:42\">ACT 5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:12\">ACT 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:20\">ACT 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:15\">ROM 10:15</a></p>\n<h3>Proclaiming the gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:16\">ROM 15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:20-Rom15:21\">ROM 15:20–15:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:5\">ACT 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:7\">ACT 15:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:17\">1CO 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:16\">1CO 9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:1-1Cor15:2\">1CO 15:1–15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:15-2Cor10:16\">2CO 10:15–10:16</a></p>\n<h3>Testifying to the truth about Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:42-Acts10:43\">ACT 10:42–10:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:35-John1:36\">JHN 1:35–1:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26-John15:27\">JHN 15:26–15:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:32-Acts2:33\">ACT 2:32–2:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:2-Acts17:3\">ACT 17:2–17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1-1John1:3\">1JN 1:1–1:3</a></p>\n<h3>Calling people to believe in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:13-Rom10:14\">ROM 10:13–10:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:14-Mark1:15\">MRK 1:14–1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:38-Acts13:39\">ACT 13:38–13:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:30-Acts16:34\">ACT 16:30–16:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:4\">ACT 18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:28\">ACT 26:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:5\">ROM 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:11\">1CO 15:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:11\">2CO 5:11</a></p>\n<h2>The context of the evangelist's work</h2>\n<h3>Missionary journeys</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:4-Acts13:5\">ACT 13:4–13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:24-Acts14:25\">ACT 14:24–14:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:9-Acts16:10\">ACT 16:9–16:10</a></p>\n<h3>In partnership with others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:1\">LUK 10:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:7\">MRK 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:23\">ACT 10:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:1\">ACT 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6\">ACT 16:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:14-Acts17:15\">ACT 17:14–17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:5\">PHP 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>Within a settled period of ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:5\">2TI 4:5</a></strong> <em>Timothy as a pastor is also to do the work of an evangelist.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:9-Acts18:11\">ACT 18:9–18:11</a> <em>Paul spends a year and a half in Corinth</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:30-Acts28:31\">ACT 28:30–28:31</a> <em>Paul preaches the gospel whilst under house arrest in Rome</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:13-1Tim4:14\">1TI 4:13–4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a></p>\n<h2>The evangelist's integrity</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:17\">2CO 2:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:12\">2CO 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:3-1Thess2:5\">1TH 2:3–2:5</a></p>\n<h2>The evangelist's commitment</h2>\n<h3>Working so as not to be a burden</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:8-1Thess2:9\">1TH 2:8–2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:33-Acts20:34\">ACT 20:33–20:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:12\">1CO 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:6\">1CO 9:6</a></p>\n<h3>Facing hardship and danger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23-2Cor11:29\">2CO 11:23–11:29</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:18\">ACT 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:23-Acts20:24\">ACT 20:23–20:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:33\">ACT 21:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:19-Eph6:20\">EPH 6:19–6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:40\">ACT 5:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:22-Acts16:23\">ACT 16:22–16:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:58\">ACT 7:58</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:19\">ACT 14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:29\">ACT 9:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:30-Acts21:31\">ACT 21:30–21:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:19\">ACT 20:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:2\">1TH 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:1-Rom9:2\">ROM 9:1–9:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:1\">ROM 10:1</a></p>\n<h2>Financial support for evangelists</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:11-1Cor9:14\">1CO 9:11–9:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:18\">1TI 5:18</a></p>\n<h2>The evangelist's blessing</h2>\n<h3>Joy at seeing the church grow</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:7-1Thess3:9\">1TH 3:7–3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:3\">ACT 15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:19-1Thess2:20\">1TH 2:19–2:20</a></p>\n<h3>The satisfaction of seeing new converts grow in their faith</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:4-1Cor1:7\">1CO 1:4–1:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:15-Eph1:16\">EPH 1:15–1:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:3-Phil1:6\">PHP 1:3–1:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:2-1Thess1:3\">1TH 1:2–1:3</a></p>",
